break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; line-break: after-white-space;"><p =
data-start=3D"2576" data-end=3D"3281">Kia ora Grant,&nbsp;</p><p =
data-start=3D"2576" data-end=3D"3281">thanks for your email and for =
proposing to bring stakeholders together. As you=E2=80=99ve said, you =
will =E2=80=9Cgather the supporting information=E2=80=A6 and provide =
that=E2=80=A6&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"2839" data-end=3D"2853">well =
ahead</strong>&nbsp;of [any] site meeting,=E2=80=9D and you=E2=80=99ll =
send an agenda based on my email. Could you please first send =
your&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"2956" data-end=3D"2977">written =
responses</strong>&nbsp;to my questions and the&nbsp;<strong =
data-start=3D"3002" data-end=3D"3026">supporting =
documents</strong>&nbsp;(reports, scope, raw notes/photo logs from prior =
attendances, and the&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"3097" =
data-end=3D"3114">test-led plan</strong>&nbsp;with methods, thresholds, =
labs and pass/fail criteria)? Once I have those, I can identify the =
appropriate experts to attend.&nbsp;</p><p data-start=3D"3288" =
data-end=3D"3452">Given I rely on third-party availability, please plan =
on&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"3345" data-end=3D"3366">1=E2=80=932 =
weeks=E2=80=99 notice</strong>&nbsp;after I receive your written =
responses and the agenda. I=E2=80=99m very happy to meet then.</p><p =
data-start=3D"3459" data-end=3D"3908">To avoid further email =
back-and-forth, please also include:<br data-start=3D"3518" =
data-end=3D"3521">=E2=80=A2&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"3525" =
data-end=3D"3548">AC2213/Council path</strong>&nbsp;(consent or written =
exemption) and confirmation of&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"3600" =
data-end=3D"3609">CPEng</strong>&nbsp;engagement;<br data-start=3D"3621" =
data-end=3D"3624">=E2=80=A2&nbsp;<strong data-start=3D"3628" =
data-end=3D"3643">Hold-points</strong>&nbsp;and clearances (roof/eaves =
intrusives, cavities, corrosion/pH-chloride, IAQ, whole-installation =
electrical to AS/NZS 3000, HVAC/gas hygiene);<br data-start=3D"3785" =
data-end=3D"3788">=E2=80=A2 Any directions provided to =
ASURNZ.&nbsp;</p><p data-start=3D"3915" data-end=3D"4042">Once received =
I=E2=80=99ll revert with attendee names and propose meeting dates within =
the 1=E2=80=932 week window.<br data-start=3D"4014" data-end=3D"4017">Ng=C4=
